{"tid":866362,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無錢無樓真係唔好拍拖？","createTime":"2018-10-17T20:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T14:55:07.000Z","uid":166948,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"145cc5ff70ed32057a521973078f09fe19f94df7","tid":866362,"uid":166948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:32:56.000Z","msg":"廿頭 就畢業<br />\n以前細個拍拖 就話兩個人開心就得<br />\n去到呢個世代同年紀 錢同樓就真係好重要<br />\n屋企之前生意失敗 父母離婚 再比人呃哂身家<br />\n宜家住緊公屋 每次拍拖都好怕女朋友會嫌棄<br />\n雖然佢地都無 但佢地太有錢<br />\n自己自卑心都過唔到<br />\n有時候ex想食貴野 我話好<br />\n但佢知對我黎講好貴 佢會揾藉口話請或者比返錢我<br />\n我寧願佢揾個更好 好想靠自己努力令身邊人開心幸福<br />\n<br />\n出到黎社會 識其他女仔 <br />\n唔係自己有錢就係個ex有錢或者比有錢人追緊<br />\n香港地 想普普通通拍拖真係好難<br />\n好想靠自己 但前路茫茫 好攰 好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107719809a3292bda4436ff92d88a90a9197b9cd","tid":866362,"uid":63117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:39:14.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"b75b7a14372285332e5f7d83ccf25a805a65ad23","tid":866362,"uid":61533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9be61fef7690b77245fee0cf6bfb105900b91c","tid":866362,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b75b7a14372285332e5f7d83ccf25a805a65ad23","tid":866362,"uid":61533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T00:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f28b8d98b355a978406d65e11a13d7872cec7fa",